01:19:43.958 --> 01:19:46.540
So this is about Peg, I gather?

01:19:46.791 --> 01:19:47.999
Yes.

01:19:48.375 --> 01:19:50.665
Then I suppose she should hear it.

01:19:52.791 --> 01:19:53.915
My son as well.

01:19:54.791 --> 01:19:57.999
We have no secrets
in this family, Miss Raton.

01:19:58.250 --> 01:19:59.707
Brian?

01:20:00.041 --> 01:20:01.665
Come here, son.

01:20:12.541 --> 01:20:15.040
I've observed some...

01:20:15.833 --> 01:20:19.249
distressing behavior
as of late, Mr. Cleek.

01:20:20.583 --> 01:20:23.540
Chris.

01:20:24.708 --> 01:20:26.665
Peggy isn't looking well.

01:20:28.166 --> 01:20:32.332
She's had to rush out to use the ladies
rest room several times during class.

01:20:33.750 --> 01:20:35.082
Her studies are off,

01:20:35.333 --> 01:20:38.040
and she's taken to wearing clothes
that are much too big for her.

01:20:42.083 --> 01:20:44.165
Well, she does like
to wear my sweats.

01:20:46.083 --> 01:20:49.332
Does Peggy have a boyfriend,
do you know, Mr. Cleek?

01:20:49.833 --> 01:20:51.165
No.

01:20:53.291 --> 01:20:55.749
And I would know if she did.

01:20:58.791 --> 01:21:00.124
Why?

01:21:01.458 --> 01:21:06.207
I believe that Peggy
is pregnant, Mr. Cleek.

01:21:11.708 --> 01:21:13.665
Pregnant.
- I am not!

01:21:19.291 --> 01:21:22.082
What makes you think that
Peggy is pregnant, Miss Raton?

01:21:22.458 --> 01:21:24.499
Well, she's showing, Mr. Cleek.

01:21:24.750 --> 01:21:28.332
Not very much right now,
but that won't last much longer.

01:21:36.250 --> 01:21:40.457
Do any of your colleagues
concur with this opinion, Miss Raton?

01:21:40.708 --> 01:21:42.999
I wouldn't know.
I haven't discussed it with them.

01:21:43.250 --> 01:21:44.582
I thought it best

01:21:44.833 --> 01:21:46.915
to come directly
to you and your wife.

01:21:47.166 --> 01:21:49.374
It was good of you to do so.

01:21:56.250 --> 01:21:58.915
I thought teachers
were supposed to listen,

01:21:59.166 --> 01:22:01.874
but you're not very good at listening,
are you, Miss Raton?

01:22:02.166 --> 01:22:04.915
Because I told you
Peggy does not have a boyfriend

01:22:05.166 --> 01:22:06.415
and that if she did
I would know about it.

01:22:06.666 --> 01:22:08.374
Did I not say that?

01:22:08.625 --> 01:22:10.832
Well, yes, but...

01:22:11.083 --> 01:22:13.040
So you're accusing Brian?

01:22:15.708 --> 01:22:19.249
He's just a boy.
- Absolutely not!

01:22:19.500 --> 01:22:21.040
So you're accusing me?

01:22:21.333 --> 01:22:22.624
No.

01:22:22.916 --> 01:22:24.124
No, I...

01:22:25.208 --> 01:22:26.582
No. You're accusing me?

01:22:26.833 --> 01:22:27.582
Dad!

01:22:27.833 --> 01:22:31.957
You come to my house and you
accuse me of something like that.

01:22:32.208 --> 01:22:34.040
I said nothing
of the sort, Mr. Cleek.

01:22:34.291 --> 01:22:35.999
I know you didn't say
anything of the sort.

01:22:36.250 --> 01:22:37.832
It's what you haven't said.

01:22:38.083 --> 01:22:39.832
You think I'm stupid?

01:22:40.541 --> 01:22:42.415
Do you think I'm stupid?

01:22:43.500 --> 01:22:45.040
No.
- Miss Raton?

01:22:47.166 --> 01:22:47.957
Yes?

01:22:48.625 --> 01:22:50.957
You don't really...

01:22:52.083 --> 01:22:55.582
think that I would want to
miss out on heaven, do you?

01:23:01.166 --> 01:23:02.749
Hey, Brian?

01:23:03.583 --> 01:23:04.957
Would you get the rope?

01:23:17.916 --> 01:23:19.040
Please!

01:23:20.166 --> 01:23:22.082
Daddy, please stop!

01:23:22.708 --> 01:23:25.165
Daddy, please, she's my teacher!

01:23:25.416 --> 01:23:28.040
Please, she's my friend, daddy!
- Your friend?

01:23:28.291 --> 01:23:29.874
Your friend, is that what you said?

01:23:30.125 --> 01:23:31.874
Well, your friend just
came to expose you

01:23:32.125 --> 01:23:34.165
for the little slut whore that you are!

01:23:35.166 --> 01:23:36.832
Daddy, you can't!

01:23:41.000 --> 01:23:43.957
You can't! You can't! You can't!

01:23:44.208 --> 01:23:46.457
I am so fucking sick

01:23:46.708 --> 01:23:50.749
of "you can't" from
the women in this family!

01:23:51.125 --> 01:23:51.999
Your mother,

01:23:52.708 --> 01:23:55.665
your idiot sisters, you!

01:23:56.500 --> 01:23:59.249
Please. Let me go.

01:23:59.500 --> 01:24:00.874
I swear I won't tell anyone.

01:24:01.125 --> 01:24:02.415
Yeah, I know you won't.

01:24:08.541 --> 01:24:09.790
You know what?

01:24:10.916 --> 01:24:12.915
Make that all women.

01:24:13.791 --> 01:24:17.165
Make that all women.
Because you're leeches,

01:24:17.541 --> 01:24:21.540
every one of you suck a man dry,

01:24:21.791 --> 01:24:26.332
who works like a dog every day
and you suck him dry!

01:24:28.375 --> 01:24:29.249
Chris...

01:24:29.625 --> 01:24:32.082
Stop it!
- Shut up, lady!

01:24:36.541 --> 01:24:38.832
Do you know what
you're good for, Peg?

01:24:39.083 --> 01:24:40.624
Do you?

01:24:41.208 --> 01:24:44.499
You and every other whining bitch,

01:24:45.041 --> 01:24:49.040
you're good for one thing
and one thing only.

01:24:49.416 --> 01:24:53.082
And half the time
you're miserable at that.

01:24:53.958 --> 01:24:56.415
You think I don't know who you are?

01:24:56.666 --> 01:24:58.582
You think I don't know?

01:24:58.875 --> 01:25:03.124
You're no different than that thing,
that thing in the cellar.

01:25:03.833 --> 01:25:05.790
That's where you all belong!

01:25:06.041 --> 01:25:08.040
Each and every cunting one of you!

01:25:21.208 --> 01:25:22.457
No!

01:25:23.291 --> 01:25:24.540
Brian,

01:25:26.000 --> 01:25:27.665
I lost my composure there.

01:25:27.916 --> 01:25:29.749
I got a little emotional.

01:25:30.000 --> 01:25:32.915
Never let emotions
get the best of you. Okay?

01:25:33.166 --> 01:25:34.582
Okay.
- Good.

01:25:36.500 --> 01:25:38.832
I want you to get the door, son.

01:25:39.083 --> 01:25:41.249
We'll handle this one right away.

01:25:41.500 --> 01:25:43.332
No! No!

01:25:48.375 --> 01:25:50.374
No, please, help me!

01:25:50.833 --> 01:25:52.332
I swear I won't tell anyone.

01:26:07.250 --> 01:26:08.749
Hold on to her!

01:26:09.291 --> 01:26:10.624
I got her, dad.

01:26:14.583 --> 01:26:15.374
Peggy?

01:26:48.125 --> 01:26:51.040
Momma, what's
happening to the doggies?

01:27:01.000 --> 01:27:03.624
It's okay, come here, honey.

01:27:08.250 --> 01:27:11.124
Go to your room and lock the door.

01:27:34.000 --> 01:27:35.749
That's a very bad idea.

01:27:37.958 --> 01:27:39.249
Bad idea.

01:27:43.625 --> 01:27:46.540
Can you say Anophthalmia?

01:27:53.208 --> 01:27:54.790
Oh, yeah, sister,
let's see what you can do!

01:27:56.291 --> 01:27:57.374
Anophthalmia!

01:29:01.666 --> 01:29:03.040
Peggy?

01:29:03.291 --> 01:29:04.999
What have you done?

01:30:36.958 --> 01:30:39.332
She doesn't even look
real anymore, does she, dad?

01:30:39.583 --> 01:30:41.249
She does to me, son.

01:31:02.166 --> 01:31:03.790
Listen, I want you
to go to the house,

01:31:04.041 --> 01:31:05.165
wake your mom up.

01:31:05.416 --> 01:31:08.499
Get some cleaning supplies,
some lawn leaf bags, okay?

01:31:08.750 --> 01:31:10.832
They're never gonna
be able to eat all this.

01:31:11.791 --> 01:31:13.082
Sure, dad.

01:31:16.000 --> 01:31:18.290
Get me a soda pop
while you're at it.

01:31:20.000 --> 01:31:22.332
Getjacked up on that caffeine.

01:32:09.000 --> 01:32:09.499
Darlin'!

01:34:06.333 --> 01:34:07.790
Stay with me, okay?

01:34:08.041 --> 01:34:09.790
I want mommy!

01:34:10.125 --> 01:34:11.790
Shit! He's got his keys!

01:34:16.250 --> 01:34:18.874
Can you hold this for me?
Don't drop that.

01:34:19.750 --> 01:34:20.915
Dammit!

01:34:22.833 --> 01:34:23.665
Shit!

01:34:23.916 --> 01:34:25.790
Hey, it's the lady and sister.

01:34:32.833 --> 01:34:36.290
Darlin'!

